The paper discusses the impact of AutoAI on the practice of data science, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The interviews with data scientists also touch upon human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as they discuss the collaboration between humans and AI systems. Finally, the paper also touches upon software engineering (cs.SE) as it discusses the potential changes in work practices for data scientists.
